alerts.description: Es tritt im Warnzeitraum oberhalb 800 m Schneefall mit Mengen zwischen 10 cm und 20 cm auf. In Staulagen werden Mengen bis 40 cm erreicht. Die Schneefallgrenze steigt auf 1000 Meter. Verbreitet wird es glatt.

There is a risk of snowfall (Level 2 of 4).
Height range: > 800 m; Precipitation amounts: 10-20 cm; in windward areas: < 40 cm; snowfall level: rising to 1000 meter

There is a risk of light snowfall (Level 1 of 4).
Precipitation amounts: 1-5 cm; snowfall level: rising to 1000 meter

There is a risk of wind gusts (level 1 of 4).
Max. gusts: < 60 km/h; Wind direction: south-west then west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations ~ 70 km/h

There is a risk of gale-force gusts (Level 2 of 4).
Height range: > 600 m; Max. gusts: 65-85 km/h; Wind direction: south-west then west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations < 100 km/h

There is a risk of storm-force gusts (Level 2 of 4).
Height range: > 1000 m; Max. gusts: 90-100 km/h; Wind direction: west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations ~ 115 km/h
